00:00:51.860 --> 00:00:57.870
&gt;&gt;Too much of our resources go into livestock
production. Every year roughly 60 million

00:00:57.870 --> 00:01:02.890
people starve to death. If America were to
reduce it's meat intake by just 10 percent

00:01:02.890 --> 00:01:05.740
those 60 million people could be adequately
fed.

00:01:05.740 --> 00:01:11.700
&gt;&gt;First, everybody of us and one euro or one
dollar or whatever you're paying in your contribute

00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:14.590
for this government.

