If the government is paid directly by us it
might start to work directly for us. Know

00:01:30.080 --> 00:01:31.080
what I'm saying.

00:01:31.080 --> 00:01:37.899
&gt;&gt;Make solar panels by the millions, in India,
Europe, America, Japan.

