00:01:39.420 --> 00:01:47.219
&gt;&gt;My solution to Davos question is that governments
around the world take more action to rid people

00:01:47.219 --> 00:01:52.069
of their complaints and mind sets, and encourage
citizens to be more eco friendly. Like giving

00:01:52.069 --> 00:01:56.909
away things like free exhaust pipe filters
and coupons on energy saving bulbs. In short,

00:01:56.909 --> 00:02:00.999
you need to start teaching people to stop
relying on the person next door to save the

00:02:00.999 --> 00:02:01.999
world.

00:02:01.999 --> 00:02:09.470
&gt;&gt;To accept and cherish in a positive, constructive
matter, the works of others. And to respect

00:02:09.470 --> 00:02:13.040
yourself by only doing constructive things.

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:17.990
&gt;&gt;We can save thousands, if not millions,
of lives by simply providing mosquito nets

00:02:17.990 --> 00:02:20.500
to malaria ridden areas around the world.

00:02:20.500 --> 00:02:24.200
&gt;&gt;We should be putting money into researching
the genetic engineering of plants so that

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:27.000
